    "Accordingly, one should find a pair of orthogonal and symplectic gauge groups across the NS5-type interface.We begin with the NS5-type interface with both sides of N D3-branes as well as O3 in x 6 < 0 and O3+ in x 6 > 0 (see figure 6).",
    "The configuration realizes N = 4 SO(2N + 1)gauge theory for x 6 < 0 and N = 4 USp(2N) ′ gauge theory for x 6 > 0.",
